---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ButtonCustom from "../components/Button.astro";
import Whyus from "../components/whyus.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <section class="py-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-cyan-900 mb-4 animate-fade-in-up"
            >
                Our Team
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up delay-200"
            >
                At Codebrand, we believe in the power of collective talent. Each
                team member brings their expertise, creativity, and commitment
                to deliver impactful projects.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 animate-fade-in-up delay-300"
        >
            <!-- Team Member -->
            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative transform transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="../photos/team-code/RamonNuila.png"
                    alt="Ramon Nuila"
                    class="w-full h-72 object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900">Ramon Nuila</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">CEO & Founder</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Full Stack Developer and digital strategist focused on
                        business growth and scalable software. He has led
                        successful projects in various areas, from software
                        development to brand creation. His mindset is zero
                        excuses, always results-driven.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative transform transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="../photos/team-code/Perez.png"
                    alt="Enrique Perez"
                    class="w-full h-72 object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900">
                        Enrique Pérez
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
                        Social Media Expert
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        Creator of functional digital experiences with over 10
                        years in the graphic design industry. His focus on
                        social media strategy and content creation makes him a
                        valuable asset to any team.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative transform transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="../photos/team-code/Mariacasco.png"
                    alt="Maria Casco"
                    class="w-full h-72 object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900">Maria Casco</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">Product Manager</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        With over 10 years of experience in the textile and
                        promotional product industry, Maria is an expert in
                        product management and brand-focused merchandise. She
                        prioritizes delivering high-quality products at highly
                        competitive prices.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative transform transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="../photos/team-code/Cmorel.png"
                    alt="Larisa Lopez"
                    class="w-full h-72 object-cover object-top group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900">
                        Larisa Lopez
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">UX/UI Expert</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        With over 8 years of experience in UX/UI, Larisa is an
                        expert in creating functional and attractive digital
                        experiences. Her focus is on research and user-centered
                        design.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden relative transform transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl"
            >
                <img
                    src="../photos/team-code/irispaola.png"
                    alt="Iris Gomez"
                    class="w-full h-72 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                />
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-900">Iris Gomez</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">
                        Project Coordinator
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                        An engineer passionate about optimizing time and
                        resources. With experience in project management and
                        team leadership, she focuses on delivering high-quality
                        projects on time. Her skills in resource management,
                        planning, and execution—along with quick
                        decision-making—make her a valuable asset to any team.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 text-center animate-fade-in-up delay-500">
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-base max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                More than a team, we are a blend of vision, discipline, and
                creativity. Every project is a challenge we face together—from
                strategy to execution.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center mt-0">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-cyan-900 mb-6">
            Ready to work with a passionate and committed team?
        </h2>
        <ButtonCustom text="Let’s Talk" href="/contact" />
    </div>
    <Whyus />
</Layout>
